   green-canopy stand provides most benefit in terms of C sequestration,
   wildfire resilience, and other ecosystem services at a point 10 years
   after severe wildfire. For forests that suffer high fire mortality,
   unsalvaged (NS) stands will retain the most carbon onsite. Published by
